a card is a thing
a card has a direction as either up or down

my-card = a new card with direction = down

to turn a card face up
	set its direction to up
to turn a card face down
	set its direction to down

turn my-card face up
expect the direction of my-card to be up

get my-card
turn it face up

to turn a card over: 
	turn the card face up
